{"tid":1477835,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發］央視：國泰接受CEO何杲辭職","createTime":"2019-08-16T09:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T12:05:21.000Z","uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"27672cd30a02e449b3266dd65b3a790093b3ae39","tid":1477835,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:13:18.000Z","msg":"央視新聞微博發出消息，國泰航空（293）已接受何杲辭任行政總裁職務，將由鄧健榮接替，盧家培辭任顧客及商務總裁職務，由林紹波接替。<br />\n<br />\n國泰早前有副機師被捕及被控暴動罪，及後中國民航局上周對國泰發出警示，促使國泰將涉嫌暴動罪的機師停飛，又解僱兩位涉洩警員航班資料的地勤員工。何杲本周一即向員工發放聲明，稱該公司任何時間有義務地遵守法律，指員工支持或參與非法抗議活動將接受紀律處分，後果包括被解僱。<br />\n<br />\n何杲發放的聲明指，對員工們過去兩個月的貢獻及專業表示非常感動，但稱會完全遵守內地民航局上周發出的通知。何杲指出，若抗議活動被視為違法，員工不應支持及參與這種抗議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190816/large/1565946094_2fb2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190816%2Flarge%2F1565946094_2fb2.jpg&h=da3af01a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190816/59939742\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190816%2F59939742&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjalzUVmWcutTvqHtF1LT7nQkc%3D&h=8af46003\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190816%2F59939742&h=77874841\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190816/59939742</a>"},{"pid":"7d4fc0c0f1d4d822f0fe9ea1c3d869483384924e","tid":1477835,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:14:39.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n可以賽後檢討，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It is now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i